(* State adjacency. Data is based on
 * https://writeonly.wordpress.com/2009/03/20/adjacency-list-of-states-of-the-united-states-us/;
 * the map uses the Mercator projection and is my own work.
 *
 *    __________________________________
 * __;      ||              |        |  \______ ,
 * \   WA   | \      MT     |   ND   \      __/ -_____                  ^_
 * |________|  \            |_________| MN /  \_    _ \                /  \
 * |         )  \   ________|         (    |    \_/ / [         ,_____/ ME }
 * |   OR   / ID ---+       |   SD    |____\_ WI / /  |_       (   | /| __/
 * /        |       |  WY   |---------|      \___| | MI |  ,~~-'NY |/_|/
 * \----+-----------+       |    NE   \  IA  _)  \--+--<_/-'-----. [__`;
 * /    |       |   +-+-----+--+_______\____/    |IN| OH  | PA  ( \===
 * \    |   NV  | UT  |        |        \   \ IL |  |____/+->---L\/
 *  \    \_     |     |   CO   | KS     | MO }_  <_/   (___/VA d_/
 *   \ CA  \_   |-----+-------++--------|_____ \/___KY_/_______{
 *    \_     \_|      |       +--+  OK  |     /___TN___/__  NC _}  __________
 *      |__    \  AZ  |  NM   |  +-_____| AR /  |   |  \SC`\__/   /    VT NH |
 *         \___/      |       |          ]__( MS|AL |   \ _/     /     MA    |
 *             ---,_____~-----+    TX    \  (__ | __| GA |      /      CT RI |
 *                        `\  __         / LA  \|_|__----|     /   DE NJ     |
 *                           –  \     __/---~__;     `-. \     | WV DC MD    |
 *                               \   /                 |FL\    |             |
 *                                \__|                  \ |    | Unlabeled   |
 *                                                       `+    | states      |
 *                                                             |_____________|
 *)
